description.name: Leaf Blower 3-functional Standard
description.long_desc:
Leaf Blower 3-functions Standard

Leaf blower is a device which enables to keep order in the garden. It is perfect for cleaning a vehicle, terrace or other parts of the garden not only from leaves but also fromáother organic waste.ááBlower is equipped with 3000 W power engine which easily deals with removing impurities.áHuge 45l leaves bagáenables to use the device for a long time with no frequent breaks for emptying wastes. Blower collets leavesáand they are crushed into 10:1 of volume.ááCrushing enables to save the space in the bag, a then be used as aácompost.áErgonomically placed handle guarantesáweight balance, and a comfortable belt enables additional comfort of work.ááBlower cleans the surface with a speed of 275 km/h air flow. Wheels mounted at the lower end of pipe make suction hose easier to be led along the ground.áSuction hose consists of two parts, because of this, blower take not much space.ááSuction functioná- leaves are chopped in order to save spare and collected in waste bag.ááBlowing functioná- leaves can be stored at one place or blown out fromáhard-to-reach places.á

á

Technical data::

Voltage: 230V/50Hz

Power: 3000W

Rotational speed: 14000rpm

Air speed: 275km/h

Max efficiency: 12.5m3/min

Waste bag: 45 L

á
